verbs.description: North Korean leader Kim Jong Un [V: has] deployed his top aide to the U.S. in preparation for the June summit with President Donald Trump . Kim Yong Chol is expected to meet with U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo , South Korea 's Yonhap News Agency reported , following his arrival at New York 's John F. Kennedy International Airport just after 2 p.m. Wednesday . Kim , 72 , a four - star general and vice chairman of North Korea ’s ruling Workers’ Party Central Committee , has been leading the nation 's diplomatic outreach . The former spy will be the highest - ranking North Korean official to visit the U.S. in nearly two decades , according to Bloomberg . In 2000 , Vice Marshal Jo Myong Rok traveled to the U.S. to meet with then - President Bill Clinton . The president has put pressure on his advisers to move quickly on plans to meet with Kim as they pursue an agreement on the steps to denuclearize North Korea . What did Trump say ? Trump …
